e;'><div>بِإِذۡنِهِۦۖ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَيُبَيِّنُ ءَايَٰتِهِۦ لِلنَّاسِ لَعَلَّهُمۡ يَتَذَكَّرُونَ </div><div>١٢٢</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَيَسۡ‍َٔلُونَكَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> عَنِ ٱلۡمَحِيضِۖ قُلۡ هُوَ <a data-content='قذر يُؤذي' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>أَذٗى</a> فَٱعۡتَزِلُواْ ٱلنِّسَآءَ </div><div>فِي</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>ٱلۡمَحِيضِ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَلَا تَقۡرَبُوهُنَّ حَتَّىٰ يَطۡهُرۡنَۖ فَإِذَا تَطَهَّرۡنَ </div><div>فَأۡتُوهُنَّ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>مِنۡ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> حَيۡثُ أَمَرَكُمُ ٱللَّهُۚ إِنَّ ٱللَّهَ يُحِبُّ ٱلتَّوَّٰبِينَ وَيُحِبُّ </div><div>ٱلۡمُتَطَهِّرِينَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>٢٢٢</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> نِسَآؤُكُمۡ <a data-content='مزرع الذرية لكم' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>حَرۡثٞ لَّكُمۡ</a> فَأۡتُواْ حَرۡثَكُمۡ <a data-content='كيف شئتم ما دام في القُبُل' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>أَنَّىٰ شِئۡتُمۡۖ</a> </div><div>وَقَدِّمُواْ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>لِأَنفُسِكُمۡۚ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَٱتَّقُواْ ٱللَّهَ وَٱعۡلَمُوٓاْ أَنَّكُم مُّلَٰقُوهُۗ </div><div>وَبَشِّرِ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>ٱلۡمُؤۡمِنِينَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ٣٢٢ وَلَا تَجۡعَلُواْ ٱللَّهَ <a data